Until early September, the most frequent [[risk factor]]s presented by the deceased patients are [[obesity]] (36.4%), [[Diabetes mellitus|diabetes]] (18.2%), [[asthma]] (18.2%), [[pregnancy]] (9.1%) and [[chronic obstructive pulmonary disease]] (6.1%).<ref name="Latest2CRI">{{cite web|url=http://www.ministeriodesalud.go.cr/emergencia_sanitaria/boletines/comunicado_oficial_influenza_pandemica_08_setiembre_2009.pdf|title=Comunicado Oficial: Situación de la Influenza Pandémica en Costa Rica al 8 de setiembre de 2009 - Boletín N. 56|author=Ministerio de Salud de Costa Rica |date=2009-09-08 |accessdate=2009-09-12|language=Spanish|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/query?id=1253135033157097|archivedate=2009-09-16|deadurl=no}}</ref>

